</db:listitem>
</db:varlistentry>
</db:variablelist>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The Qt 3D module provides the foundations and core types used for near-realtime simulations built on the Qt 3D framework.</db:para>
</db:section>
